highlights.text: “POPSTAR (feat. Drake)” by DJ Khaled and Drake is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #7.
Juice WRLD has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Come & Go (with Marshmello)” is the highest at #6.
“Shape of You” by Ed Sheeran has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 185 weeks straight.
“Head & Heart (feat. MNEK)” by Joel Corry and MNEK is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 106 spots at #64.
